<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fractured Mind // System Configuration</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0d0e12; color: #d1d5db; font-family: monospace; padding: 20px; }
        .config-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #1a1c23; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #2e3244; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #a78bfa; font-weight: bold; }
        .form-group input, .form-group textarea { width: 100%; padding: 10px; background: #111318; border: 1px solid #4338ca; color: #fff; box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 4px; }
        .btn-save { background: #4338ca; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 20px; width: 100%; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.1rem; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; }
        .btn-save:hover { background: #4f46e5; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main class="config-container">
        <h1>⚙️ Overwrite Core Engine Config</h1>
        <p>Values updated here will instantly inject into the next live runtime.</p>

        <form action="/admin/update" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Rooms Required Until Boss Encouter</label>
                <input type="number" name="levelsUntilBoss" value="4" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Player Max Health</label>
                <input type="number" name="playerMaxHealth" value="100" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Player Melee Damage Output</label>
                <input type="number" name="playerMeleeDamage" value="10" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Enemy Baseline Health (Minor Ghosts)</label>
                <input type="number" name="enemyBaseHealth" value="30" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Enemy Damage Output (Minor Ghosts)</label>
                <input type="number" name="enemyDamage" value="10" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Global Network Broadcast (Home Screen Message)</label>
                <textarea name="announcementText" rows="3" required>All systems operational.</textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-save">Inject Configuration Update</button>
        </form>

        <br>
        <a href="/admin" style="color: #818cf8; text-decoration: none;">&lt; Back to Dashboard</a>
    </main>

</body>
</html>